arr.name: description_ssm
arr.str: Tenants-in-chief and their geld (tax) assessments recorded in the 'satellite' text known as the Yorkshire Summary, a quasi-index to the Yorkshire folios included in the manuscript of Domesday Book. Some of the names and many of the assessments differ from those recorded in Domesday Book itself; the differences are documented in the database. This is the first publication of the electronic data.
